+# SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
+config PVR2_DC
+	bool "Sega Dreamcast PowerVR2 tile-accelerator submission device"
+	depends on SH_DREAMCAST
+	default y
+	help
+	  Char device /dev/pvr that exposes the PowerVR2 VRAM, register block and
+	  tile-accelerator input FIFO to userland, plus blocking vblank and
+	  end-of-render waits.  It provides the plumbing for a userland 3D stack
+	  (libpvr/GLdc) and coexists with the pvr2fb framebuffer driver.
+
+	  If unsure, say Y on Dreamcast.
